{
  "id": "indus_cisi_structural",
  "name": "Indus CISI: Structural Analysis on Real Multi-Sign Inscriptions (Parpola)",
  "description": "P1: Full structural atlas of the CISI corpus (179 Mohenjo-daro inscriptions, 1,003 tokens, 182 distinct Parpola signs). Unlike BuiltinCorpus('indus') which returns single-sign sequences, indus_cisi provides real multi-sign inscription sequences enabling meaningful positional profiling (I/M/T rates per sign), bigram statistics, and writing system classification. Source: mayig/indus-valley-script-corpus (MIT, 2024-2025).",
